i-dark:#BD976A\"> alt</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div></template>\n</Tabs>\n<div class=\"hint-container caution\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">标签嵌套</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>p 和 h标题不能相互嵌套</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>p里面不能包含div</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hint-container warning\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">注意</p>\n<p>CSS继承性并不能全部继承父级全部属性</p>\n</div>\n<iframe class=\"js-fiddle-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"width:100%;height:14rem;margin:16px auto;border:none;border-radius:5px;\" title=\"JS Fiddle\" src=\"https://jsfiddle.net/passwordgloo/hckug6w8/embedded/css,html,result/dark/\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\"></iframe>","tagOpen":"<template>","tagClose":"</template>"},"script":null,"scriptSetup":null,"scripts":[],"styles":[],"customBlocks":[]},"content":"![](/body/green_2.webp)\n\n@[pdf](https://file.iglooblog.top/pdf/day04%EF%BC%88CSS02-%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%99%A8%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%2B%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%2B%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%2B%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%89v1.0.pdf)\n\n## 复合选择器\n\n### 后代选择器\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"9rem\"](passwordgloo/goeLuq2z/)\n\n### 子代选择器\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"12rem\"](passwordgloo/98w0uenj/)\n\n### 并集选择器\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"11rem\"](passwordgloo/b9gupk2v/)\n\n### 交集选择器\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"13rem\"](passwordgloo/dqohvw21/)\n\n::: info hover悬浮效果\n\n:::\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"11rem\"](passwordgloo/k3Lrzsen/)\n\n## Emmet语法\n\n| 记忆       | 示例            | 效果                                 |\n| ---------- | --------------- | ------------------------------------ |\n| 标签名     | div             | `<div></div>`                       |\n| 类选择器   | .red            | `<div class=\"red\"></div>`|\n| id选择器   | #one            | `<div id=\"one\"></div>`|\n| 交集选择器 | p.red#one       | `<p class=\"red\" id=\"one\"></p>`|\n| 子代选择器 | ul>li           | `<ul><li></li></ul>`|\n| 内部文本   | ul>li(li的内容) | `<ul><li>li的内容</li></ul>`|\n| 创建多个   | ul>li*3         | `<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul> `|\n\n## 背景\n\n### background-color\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"15rem\"](passwordgloo/x2fhmt5z/)\n\n### background-image\n\n::: normal-demo\n\n```html\n<div>文字</div>\n```\n\n```css\ndiv {\n  width: 200px;\n  height:200px;\n  /* 会被下面的image属性覆盖掉 */\n  background-color: orange;\n  background-image: url(/html/dog.gif);\n}\n```\n\n:::\n\n### background-repeat\n\n::: normal-demo\n\n```html\n<div>文字</div>\n```\n\n```css\ndiv {\n  width: 400px;\n  height:200px;\n  background-image: url(/css/quanquan.png);\n  background-repeat: repeat-x;\n}\n```\n\n:::\n\n### background-position\n\n::: normal-demo\n\n```html\n<div>文字</div>\n```\n\n```css\ndiv {\n  width: 600px;\n  height:200px;\n  background-image: url(/html/dog.gif);\n  /* 禁止重复 */\n  background-repeat: no-repeat;\n  background-position: -50px -100px;\n}\n```\n\n:::\n\n::: tip background复合写法\n\n:::\n\n```css{4,9}\n/* 不分先后顺序 背景色  背景图  背景图平铺  背景图位置 */\n/* background: pink url(/html/dog.gif) no-repeat center bottom; */\n/* 背景图位置如果是英文单词可以颠倒顺序 */\nbackground: pink url(/html/dog.gif) no-repeat bottom center ;\n\n/* 测试背景图位置如果是数值 不要颠倒顺序 */\n/* 水平50px, 垂直100px */\n/* background: pink url(/html/dog.gif) no-repeat 50px 100px; */\nbackground: pink url(/html/dog.gif) no-repeat 100px 50px;\n```\n\n## display\n\n::: tabs\n\n@tab 行内\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"14rem\"](passwordgloo/s90Lpnr2/)\n\n@tab 块\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"23rem\"](passwordgloo/0mhae9bk/)\n\n@tab 行内块\n\n```css\nimg {\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n}\n```\n\n```html\n<img src=\"./css/quanquan.png\" alt=\"\">\n<img src=\"./css/quanquan.png\" alt=\"\">\n```\n\n:::\n\n::: danger 标签嵌套\n\n- p 和 h标题不能相互嵌套\n\n- p里面不能包含div\n\n:::\n\n> [!warning]\n>\n> CSS继承性并不能全部继承父级全部属性\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"14rem\"](passwordgloo/hckug6w8/)","excerpt":"","tasklists":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"复合选择器","slug":"复合选择器","link":"#复合选择器","children":[{"level":3,"title":"后代选择器","slug":"后代选择器","link":"#后代选择器","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"子代选择器","slug":"子代选择器","link":"#子代选择器","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"并集选择器","slug":"并集选择器","link":"#并集选择器","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"交集选择器","slug":"交集选择器","link":"#交集选择器","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"Emmet语法","slug":"emmet语法","link":"#emmet语法","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"背景","slug":"背景","link":"#背景","children":[{"level":3,"title":"background-color","slug":"background-color","link":"#background-color","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"background-image","slug":"background-image","link":"#background-image","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"background-repeat","slug":"background-repeat","link":"#background-repeat","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"background-position","slug":"background-position","link":"#background-position","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"display","slug":"display","link":"#display","children":[]}]}}
